<#602828>:Unique Trait:</>		"Adrenaline Thrush"
Bernie can call for assistance from Jimmy and Lee, who each
have their own cooldown timers. Additionally, Bernie's Craze
Technique, Rambling Inventory, can search for, store, and use
one of 6 weapons as different attacks.
Landing hits generates Bernie's Adrenaline Thrush meter.
Jimmy and Lee's cooldowns consume this meter to reduce
faster, and Rambling Inventory consumes this meter to
search through weapons faster. Counter Hits generate
significantly more meter.

